claim.claim-text:
An optical modulator comprising:
a substrate that has an electro-optical effect;
an optical waveguide that includes a Mach-Zehnder type optical waveguide formed in the substrate;
a modulation electrode that modulates light waves propagating in the optical waveguide;
an optical fiber that guides an output light from the optical waveguide;
light collecting means for collecting two radiated lights from the Mach-Zehnder type optical waveguide toward a single optical receiving element; and
light intensity ratio adjustingmeans for adjusting a light intensity ratio of the two radiated lights received by the optical receiving element.
